items.desc: Azealia Banks is a wiki, that is dedicated all about  the American rapper  and  singer  Azealia Banks!We are the perfect place for Azealia's fans!Here you can learn all about her songs,her singles,her music videos,her EP ("1991"),her mixtape ("Fantasea") and her debut album ("Broke with Expensive Taste")!Feel free to join us!
